Task
Is at least one of the two function arguments an array?
Write a function isArrayInArg that takes two values value1 and value2 as arguments and returns true if at least one of the arguments is an array, and false otherwise.
Example:
• the isArrayInArg (12, [1]) function must return true;
• the isArrayInArg ([], "Welcome") function must return true;
• the isArrayInArg ([1], [0]) function must return true;
• the isArrayInArg (15, 0) function must return false;
• the isArrayInArg ({name: 'Alice'}, "Bob") function must return false.

Solution
function isArrayInArg (value1, value2) {
 if (Array.isArray (value1) || Array.isArray (value2)) return true;
  return false;
}
